# Problem 2 - Check Even or Odd

## Description
Given an integer N, print Even if it is even, otherwise print Odd.

## Input Format
Single integer N

## Output Format
Even or Odd

## Examples
Input: 4
Output: Even

Input: 7
Output: Odd

## Constraints
-10^6 <= N <= 10^6
Time Limit: 2 seconds
Memory Limit: 256MB
